<div class="text-center">
  <span class="eyebrow">Access</span>
  <h2 class="mt-5 text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white">
    Pricing
  </h2>
  <div class="mt-8 inline-block surface-card px-10 py-8">
    <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-[var(--color-accent)]">Free*</p>
    <p class="mt-4 copy-muted max-w-md">
      DEVS is practical, non-accredited training focused on job-ready skills.
      Access is currently free while we grow the program.
    </p>
    <p class="mt-2 text-xs copy-subtle">*Subject to change.</p>
    <a
      href="#notify"
      class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center justify-center rounded-lg border border-[var(--color-accent)]/50 bg-[var(--color-accent-ghost)] px-4 py-2.5 text-sm font-semibold text-[var(--color-accent)] hover:border-[var(--color-accent)] hover:bg-[var(--color-accent-subtle)] transition-colors"
    >
      Join early access <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
